Description.Text: The hotel is located at Punta Cancun, near to the Convention Centre and Plaza Caracol Mall, walking distance from the Cancun Nightlife. The airport is twenty miles away.
The Junior Suites Ocean view rooms are very large in size are all in very good condition.
The hotel three restaurants serve a wide variety of foods from a snack to a gourmet Mexican cuisine, and are all located on the ground floor of the hotel, plus a snack bar at pool area.
Very large in size with plenty of seating areas, and an impressive ten meter recepetion desk.
